{
  "stem": "20848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The name of the, of the parents was Francusz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the name of the, of the married couple, young married couple, was Lerner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that's how we found out where they're taking the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because the Germans came back and they told this to men, that there is no money in the world that can buy back those women because the train went to Treblinka, and everybody that was unloaded from the train was killed.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that's my father knew we were the first people in the Warsaw ghetto to know-- one of the first people-- to know what the Jew, doing with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And therefore, my father had developed a, a policy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he said to us, as little as we were, but I understood and that saved my life many times.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He said, remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Whatever the Germans tell you to do, you do the opposite.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because if you do what they tell you to do, you're going to die.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they were making the ghetto smaller and smaller because they were forever sending people away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started working for a-- they only now kept people who were working for Germans in factories and producing something for Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we smuggled him all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We smuggled him to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We worked in a factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In a socks factory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called Schultz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Small Schultz, because there was a large Schultz who was making different things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by that time, we didn't live anymore in Rgrodewa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We live, lived in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lashna ?] 76.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And funnily enough, the factory-- it's really a very funny coincidence.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
